Specific Uses For Product
Wall Plate Cover for Ecobee Smart Thermostats
  • Please Note: Your ecobee thermostat will come with an original wall plate. Unlike the original equipped bracket, our gorgeous decorative Ecobee4 wall plate with elegant matte surface perfectly creates a modern and stylish look, covers up the previous hole or mark. Rounded edges resist dust accumulation.
  • Our wall plate ONLY works with Ecobee 4 Thermostat (EB-STATE4-01) and Ecobee SmartThermostat (EB-STATE5-01). It will not fit any other Ecobee Thermostat. Please check your Thermostat model firstly before purchasing it.
  • Installation can be finished in a few minutes. No need to paint or do any remodeling work to install the wall plate for Ecobee smart thermostat.
  • Our Ecobee wall mounting plate made of polycarbonate material to provide durability, flexibility, and resilience to withstand any heavy force.
  • Package including 6.7*6.7 inches (17*17 CM) Ecobee wall plate and screw sets. Note: The Ecobee Thermostat is not included.

Product description

Installation

1. Drill two holes on the wall and install the expansion tube into the holes.

2. Align the wall plate with the the thermostat panel.

3. Screws through the expansion tube to fix the wall plate and the thermostat panel.

4. Put the thermostat on the panel of the thermostat.
